401 inline float getManhattanDistanceTo(float inX, float inY)
402 {
403 if (leftX < inX && inX <= rightX && bottomY < inY && inY <= topY)
404 {
405 return 0;
406 }
407 if (leftX < inX && inX <= rightX)
408 {
409 return std::min(std::fabs(inY - topY), std::fabs(inY - bottomY));
410 }
411 if (bottomY < inY && inY <= topY)
412 {
413 return std::min(std::fabs(inX - leftX), std::fabs(inX - rightX));
414 }
415 return std::min(std::fabs(inX - leftX), std::fabs(inX - rightX)) +
416 std::min(std::fabs(inY - topY), std::fabs(inY - bottomY));
417 }

580 inline float getRealUtilizationRate()
581 {
582 if (cells.size())
583 {
584 std::vector<DesignInfo::DesignCell *> cellVec;
585 cellVec.clear();
586 for (auto cell : cells)
587 {
588 cellVec.push_back(cell);
589 }
590 if (cellVec[0]->isLUT())
591 {
592 float tmputilization = 0;
593 for (auto cell : cells)
594 {
595 if (cell->isLUT6())
596 tmputilization += 2.0;
597 else
598 tmputilization += 1;
599 }
600 return (float)tmputilization / capacity;
601 }
602 else
603 {
604 return getUtilizationRate();
605 }
606 }
607 return 0;
608 }

1064 inline void setSpreadLocation(float x, float y, float forgetRatio)
1065 {
1066 assert(!locked);
1067
1068 if (lastSpreadX > -100 && lastSpreadY > -100)
1069 {
1070 assert(forgetRatio <= 1);
1071 x = x * forgetRatio + lastSpreadX * (1 - forgetRatio);
1072 y = y * forgetRatio + lastSpreadY * (1 - forgetRatio);
1073 // lastSpreadX = x;
1074 // lastSpreadY = y;
1075 }
1076 lastAnchorX = x;
1077 lastAnchorY = y;
1078 anchorX = x;
1079 anchorY = y;
1080 }
1081
1090 inline void setSpreadLocation_WithLimitDisplacement(float x, float y, float forgetRatio,
1091 float limitDisplacement)
1092 {
1093 assert(!locked);
1094
1095 if (lastSpreadX > -100 && lastSpreadY > -100)
1096 {
1097 assert(forgetRatio <= 1);
1098 float disX = std::fabs(x - lastSpreadX) * forgetRatio;
1099 float disY = std::fabs(x - lastSpreadX) * forgetRatio;
1100 float dis = std::sqrt(disX * disX + disY * disY);
1101 if (dis / limitDisplacement > 1)
1102 forgetRatio /= (dis / limitDisplacement);
1103
1104 x = x * forgetRatio + lastSpreadX * (1 - forgetRatio);
1105 y = y * forgetRatio + lastSpreadY * (1 - forgetRatio);
1106
1107 // lastSpreadX = x;
1108 // lastSpreadY = y;
1109 }
1110 lastAnchorX = x;
1111 lastAnchorY = y;
1112 anchorX = x;
1113 anchorY = y;
1114 }

1874 PlacementNet(DesignInfo::DesignNet *designNet, int id, std::vector<PlacementUnit *> &cellId2PlacementUnitVec,
1875 PlacementInfo *placementInfo)

1877 {
1878 unitsOfNetPins.clear();

1885 unitsOfNetPins.push_back(tmpPU);

1889 {
1890 unitsOfDriverPins.push_back(tmpPU);

1893 {
1894 unitsOfPinsBeDriven.push_back(tmpPU);

1898 {
1899 pinOffset tmpPinOffset = pinOffset(curPin->getOffsetXInCell(), curPin->getOffsetYInCell());
1900 pinOffsetsInUnit.push_back(tmpPinOffset);
1901 }
1902 else if (tmpPU->getType() == PlacementUnitType_Macro)
1903 {
1904 PlacementMacro *tmpM = dynamic_cast<PlacementMacro *>(tmpPU);
1905 assert(tmpM);
1906 pinOffset tmpPinOffset =
1907 pinOffset(curPin->getOffsetXInCell() + tmpM->getCellOffsetXInMacro(curPin->getCell()),
1908 curPin->getOffsetYInCell() + tmpM->getCellOffsetYInMacro(curPin->getCell()));
1909 pinOffsetsInUnit.push_back(tmpPinOffset);
1910 }
1911 }
1912 leftPuId = rightPuId = topPuId = bottomPuId = -1;
1913 }

1994 inline bool updateNetBounds(bool updateX, bool updateY)
1995 {
1996 if (updateX)
1997 {
1998 leftPUX = 1e5;
1999 rightPUX = -1e5;
2000 leftPinX = 1e5;
2001 rightPinX = -1e5;
2002 for (unsigned int pinId_net = 0; pinId_net < unitsOfNetPins.size(); pinId_net++)
2003 {
2004 auto tmpPU = unitsOfNetPins[pinId_net];
2005 auto tmpPUId = tmpPU->getId();
2006 auto tmpPinOffset = pinOffsetsInUnit[pinId_net];
2007 float cellX = tmpPU->X();
2008 float pinX = tmpPU->X() + tmpPinOffset.x;
2009 if (pinX < leftPinX)
2010 {
2011 leftPinX = pinX;
2012 leftPUX = cellX;
2013 leftPuId = tmpPUId;
2014 leftPinId_net = pinId_net;
2015 }
2016 if (pinX > rightPinX)
2017 {
2018 rightPinX = pinX;
2019 rightPUX = cellX;
2020 rightPuId = tmpPUId;
2021 rightPinId_net = pinId_net;
2022 }
2023 }
2024 }
2025 if (updateY)
2026 {
2027 topPUY = -1e5;
2028 bottomPUY = 1e5;
2029 topPinY = -1e5;
2030 bottomPinY = 1e5;
2031 for (unsigned int pinId_net = 0; pinId_net < unitsOfNetPins.size(); pinId_net++)
2032 {
2033 auto tmpPU = unitsOfNetPins[pinId_net];
2034 auto tmpPUId = tmpPU->getId();
2035 auto tmpPinOffset = pinOffsetsInUnit[pinId_net];
2036 float cellY = tmpPU->Y();
2037 float pinY = tmpPU->Y() + tmpPinOffset.y;
2038 if (pinY < bottomPinY)
2039 {
2040 bottomPinY = pinY;
2041 bottomPUY = cellY;
2042 bottomPuId = tmpPUId;
2043 bottomPinId_net = pinId_net;
2044 }
2045 if (pinY > topPinY)
2046 {
2047 topPinY = pinY;
2048 topPUY = cellY;
2049 topPuId = tmpPUId;
2050 topPinId_net = pinId_net;
2051 }
2052 }
2053 }
2054 return (updateX && (leftPuId != rightPuId)) || (updateY && (topPuId != bottomPuId));
2055 }

2081 inline float getNewHPWLByTrying(PlacementUnit *curPU, double targetPUX, double targetPUY, float y2xRatio) const
2082 {
2083 float tmp_leftX = 1e5;
2084 float tmp_rightX = -1e5;
2085 float tmp_topY = -1e5;
2086 float tmp_bottomY = 1e5;
2087
2088 for (unsigned int pinId_net = 0; pinId_net < unitsOfNetPins.size(); pinId_net++)
2089 {
2090 auto tmpPU = unitsOfNetPins[pinId_net];
2091 auto tmpPinOffset = pinOffsetsInUnit[pinId_net];
2092 float pinX;
2093 if (tmpPU == curPU)
2094 {
2095 pinX = targetPUX + tmpPinOffset.x;
2096 }
2097 else
2098 {
2099 pinX = tmpPU->X() + tmpPinOffset.x;
2100 }
2101 if (pinX < tmp_leftX)
2102 {
2103 tmp_leftX = pinX;
2104 }
2105 if (pinX > tmp_rightX)
2106 {
2107 tmp_rightX = pinX;
2108 }
2109 }
2110 for (unsigned int pinId_net = 0; pinId_net < unitsOfNetPins.size(); pinId_net++)
2111 {
2112 auto tmpPU = unitsOfNetPins[pinId_net];
2113 auto tmpPinOffset = pinOffsetsInUnit[pinId_net];
2114 float pinY;
2115 if (tmpPU == curPU)
2116 {
2117 pinY = targetPUY + tmpPinOffset.y;
2118 }
2119 else
2120 {
2121 pinY = tmpPU->Y() + tmpPinOffset.y;
2122 }
2123 if (pinY < tmp_bottomY)
2124 {
2125 tmp_bottomY = pinY;
2126 }
2127 if (pinY > tmp_topY)
2128 {
2129 tmp_topY = pinY;
2130 }
2131 }
2132
2133 int A_ClockRegionY, A_ClockRegionX;
2134 placementInfo->getDeviceInfo()->getClockRegionByLocation(tmp_rightX, tmp_bottomY, A_ClockRegionX,
2135 A_ClockRegionY);
2136 std::pair<int, int> A_ClockLocYX(A_ClockRegionY, A_ClockRegionX);
2137
2138 int B_cellClockRegionY, B_cellClockRegionX;
2139 placementInfo->getDeviceInfo()->getClockRegionByLocation(tmp_leftX, tmp_topY, B_cellClockRegionX,
2140 B_cellClockRegionY);
2141 std::pair<int, int> B_ClockLocYX(B_cellClockRegionY, B_cellClockRegionX);
2142
2143 float clockRegionOverhead = 0;
2144 // if (B_ClockLocYX != A_ClockLocYX)
2145 // {
2146 // clockRegionOverhead = std::abs(B_cellClockRegionX - A_ClockRegionX) * 15;
2147 // }
2148
2149 return std::fabs(tmp_rightX - tmp_leftX) + y2xRatio * std::fabs(tmp_topY - tmp_bottomY) +
2150 clockRegionOverhead;
2151 }

2172 inline void updateBound2BoundNetWeight(std::vector<Eigen::Triplet<float>> &objectiveMatrixTripletList,
2173 std::vector<float> &objectiveMatrixDiag,
2174 Eigen::VectorXd &objectiveVector, float generalWeight, float y2xRatio,
2175 bool updateX, bool updateY, bool checkClockRegion = false)
2176 {
2177 assert(updateX ^ updateY);
2178 if (pinOffsetsInUnit.size() <= 1)
2179 return;
2180 float w = 2.0 * generalWeight / (float)(pinOffsetsInUnit.size() - 1);
2181 int nPins = pinOffsetsInUnit.size();
2182
2183 // adopt netDegree Weight from RippeFPGA
2184 if (nPins < 10)
2185 w *= 1.00;
2186 else if (nPins < 20)
2187 w *= 1.2;
2188 else if (nPins < 50)
2189 w *= 1.6;
2190 else if (nPins < 100)
2191 w *= 1.8;
2192 else if (nPins < 200)
2193 w *= 2.1;
2194 else
2195 w *= 2.5;
2196
2197 float tmp_rightX = getRightPinX(), tmp_bottomY = getBottomPinY(), tmp_leftX = getLeftPinX(),
2198 tmp_topY = getTopPinY();
2199
2200 int A_ClockRegionY, A_ClockRegionX;
2201 placementInfo->getDeviceInfo()->getClockRegionByLocation(tmp_rightX, tmp_bottomY, A_ClockRegionX,
2202 A_ClockRegionY);
2203 std::pair<int, int> A_ClockLocYX(A_ClockRegionY, A_ClockRegionX);
2204
2205 int B_cellClockRegionY, B_cellClockRegionX;
2206 placementInfo->getDeviceInfo()->getClockRegionByLocation(tmp_leftX, tmp_topY, B_cellClockRegionX,
2207 B_cellClockRegionY);
2208 std::pair<int, int> B_ClockLocYX(B_cellClockRegionY, B_cellClockRegionX);
2209
2210 float clockRegionW = 0;
2211
2212 w *= designNet->getOverallEnhanceRatio();
2213 if (updateX)
2214 {
2215 if (checkClockRegion && B_cellClockRegionX != A_ClockRegionX)
2216 {
2217 clockRegionW = 1 + std::abs(B_cellClockRegionX - A_ClockRegionX) * 32 /
2218 (float)(pinOffsetsInUnit.size() - 1) * 0.01;
2219 if (clockRegionW > 3)
2220 clockRegionW = 3;
2221 // w *= clockRegionW;
2222 }
2223
2224 // add net between left node and right node
2225 addB2BNet(objectiveMatrixTripletList, objectiveMatrixDiag, objectiveVector, leftPuId, rightPuId,
2226 leftPUX, rightPUX, pinOffsetsInUnit[leftPinId_net].x, pinOffsetsInUnit[rightPinId_net].x,
2227 !unitsOfNetPins[leftPinId_net]->isFixed(), !unitsOfNetPins[rightPinId_net]->isFixed(),
2228 designNet->getPinPairEnhanceRatio(leftPinId_net, rightPinId_net) * w /
2229 std::max(minDist, rightPinX - leftPinX));
2230
2231 // add net between internal node and left/right node
2232 for (unsigned int pinId_net = 0; pinId_net < unitsOfNetPins.size(); pinId_net++)
2233 {
2234 auto tmpPU = unitsOfNetPins[pinId_net];
2235 auto tmpPUId = tmpPU->getId();
2236 auto tmpPinOffset = pinOffsetsInUnit[pinId_net];
2237 float curX = tmpPU->X();
2238 bool movable = !tmpPU->isFixed();
2239 if (pinId_net != leftPinId_net && pinId_net != rightPinId_net)
2240 {
2241 addB2BNet(objectiveMatrixTripletList, objectiveMatrixDiag, objectiveVector, tmpPUId, leftPuId,
2242 curX, leftPUX, tmpPinOffset.x, pinOffsetsInUnit[leftPinId_net].x, movable,
2243 !unitsOfNetPins[leftPinId_net]->isFixed(),
2244 designNet->getPinPairEnhanceRatio(pinId_net, leftPinId_net) * w /
2245 std::max(minDist, (curX + tmpPinOffset.x) - leftPinX));
2246 addB2BNet(objectiveMatrixTripletList, objectiveMatrixDiag, objectiveVector, tmpPUId, rightPuId,
2247 curX, rightPUX, tmpPinOffset.x, pinOffsetsInUnit[rightPinId_net].x, movable,
2248 !unitsOfNetPins[rightPinId_net]->isFixed(),
2249 designNet->getPinPairEnhanceRatio(pinId_net, rightPinId_net) * w /
2250 std::max(minDist, rightPinX - (curX + tmpPinOffset.x)));
2251 }
2252 }
2253 }
2254 if (updateY)
2255 {
2256
2257 w *= y2xRatio;
2258
2259 // add net between top node and bottom node
2260 addB2BNet(objectiveMatrixTripletList, objectiveMatrixDiag, objectiveVector, bottomPuId, topPuId,
2261 bottomPUY, topPUY, pinOffsetsInUnit[bottomPinId_net].y, pinOffsetsInUnit[topPinId_net].y,
2262 !unitsOfNetPins[bottomPinId_net]->isFixed(), !unitsOfNetPins[topPinId_net]->isFixed(),
2263 designNet->getPinPairEnhanceRatio(topPinId_net, bottomPinId_net) * w /
2264 std::max(minDist, topPinY - bottomPinY));
2265
2266 // add net between internal node and top/bottom node
2267 for (unsigned int pinId_net = 0; pinId_net < unitsOfNetPins.size(); pinId_net++)
2268 {
2269 auto tmpPU = unitsOfNetPins[pinId_net];
2270 auto tmpPUId = tmpPU->getId();
2271 auto tmpPinOffset = pinOffsetsInUnit[pinId_net];
2272 float curY = tmpPU->Y();
2273 bool movable = !tmpPU->isFixed();
2274 if (pinId_net != topPinId_net && pinId_net != bottomPinId_net)
2275 {
2276 addB2BNet(objectiveMatrixTripletList, objectiveMatrixDiag, objectiveVector, tmpPUId, bottomPuId,
2277 curY, bottomPUY, tmpPinOffset.y, pinOffsetsInUnit[bottomPinId_net].y, movable,
2278 !unitsOfNetPins[bottomPinId_net]->isFixed(),
2279 designNet->getPinPairEnhanceRatio(pinId_net, bottomPinId_net) * w /
2280 std::max(minDist, (curY + tmpPinOffset.y) - bottomPinY));
2281 addB2BNet(objectiveMatrixTripletList, objectiveMatrixDiag, objectiveVector, tmpPUId, topPuId,
2282 curY, topPUY, tmpPinOffset.y, pinOffsetsInUnit[topPinId_net].y, movable,
2283 !unitsOfNetPins[topPinId_net]->isFixed(),
2284 designNet->getPinPairEnhanceRatio(pinId_net, topPinId_net) * w /
2285 std::max(minDist, topPinY - (curY + tmpPinOffset.y)));
2286 }
2287 }
2288 }
2289 }

2291 inline void addPseudoNet_enhancePin2Pin(std::vector<Eigen::Triplet<float>> &objectiveMatrixTripletList,
2292 std::vector<float> &objectiveMatrixDiag,
2293 Eigen::VectorXd &objectiveVector, float generalWeight, float y2xRatio,
2294 bool updateX, bool updateY, int PUIdA, int PUIdB, int pinIdA_net,
2295 int pinIdB_net)
2296 {
2297 float w = generalWeight;
2298
2299 if (updateX)
2300 {
2301 // add net between left node and right node
2302 addB2BNet(objectiveMatrixTripletList, objectiveMatrixDiag, objectiveVector, PUIdA, PUIdB,
2303 unitsOfNetPins[pinIdA_net]->X(), unitsOfNetPins[pinIdB_net]->X(),
2304 pinOffsetsInUnit[pinIdA_net].x, pinOffsetsInUnit[pinIdB_net].x,
2305 !unitsOfNetPins[pinIdA_net]->isFixed(), !unitsOfNetPins[pinIdB_net]->isFixed(), w);
2306 }
2307 if (updateY)
2308 {
2309 w *= y2xRatio;
2310
2311 // add net between top node and bottom node
2312 addB2BNet(objectiveMatrixTripletList, objectiveMatrixDiag, objectiveVector, PUIdA, PUIdB,
2313 unitsOfNetPins[pinIdA_net]->Y(), unitsOfNetPins[pinIdB_net]->Y(),
2314 pinOffsetsInUnit[pinIdA_net].y, pinOffsetsInUnit[pinIdB_net].y,
2315 !unitsOfNetPins[pinIdA_net]->isFixed(), !unitsOfNetPins[pinIdB_net]->isFixed(), w);
2316 }

2341 inline void addB2BNet(std::vector<Eigen::Triplet<float>> &objectiveMatrixTripletList,
2342 std::vector<float> &objectiveMatrixDiag, Eigen::VectorXd &objectiveVector, int puId0,
2343 int puId1, float pos0, float pos1, float pinOffset0, float pinOffset1, bool movable0,
2344 bool movable1, float w)
2345 {
2346 // min_x 0.5 * x'Px + q'x
2347 // s.t. l <= Ax <= u
2348 if (puId0 == puId1)
2349 return;
2350 if (movable0 && movable1)
2351 {
2352 // x0^2 + x1^2 - 2x0x1 + 2(x0c-x1c)x0 + 2(x1c-x0c)x1
2353 // objectiveMatrixTripletList.push_back(Eigen::Triplet<float>(puId0, puId0, w));
2354 // objectiveMatrixTripletList.push_back(Eigen::Triplet<float>(puId1, puId1, w));
2355 objectiveMatrixDiag[puId0] += w;
2356 objectiveMatrixDiag[puId1] += w;
2357 objectiveMatrixTripletList.push_back(Eigen::Triplet<float>(puId0, puId1, -w));
2358 objectiveMatrixTripletList.push_back(Eigen::Triplet<float>(puId1, puId0, -w));
2359 if (fabs(pinOffset0) > eps || fabs(pinOffset1) > eps)
2360 {
2361 // 2(x0c-x1c)x0 + 2(x1c-x0c)x1
2362 objectiveVector[puId0] += w * (pinOffset0 - pinOffset1);
2363 objectiveVector[puId1] += w * (pinOffset1 - pinOffset0);
2364 }
2365 }
2366 else if (movable0)
2367 {
2368 // x0^2 - 2x0x1 + 2(x0c-x1c)x0
2369 // objectiveMatrixTripletList.push_back(Eigen::Triplet<float>(puId0, puId0, w));
2370 objectiveMatrixDiag[puId0] += w;
2371 objectiveVector[puId0] += -w * pos1;
2372 if (fabs(pinOffset0) > eps || fabs(pinOffset1) > eps)
2373 {
2374 // 2(x0c-x1c)x0
2375 objectiveVector[puId0] += w * (pinOffset0 - pinOffset1);
2376 }
2377 }
2378 else if (movable1)
2379 {
2380 // x1^2 - 2x0x1 + 2(x1c-x0c)x1
2381 // objectiveMatrixTripletList.push_back(Eigen::Triplet<float>(puId1, puId1, w));
2382 objectiveMatrixDiag[puId1] += w;
2383 objectiveVector[puId1] += -w * pos0;
2384 if (fabs(pinOffset0) > eps || fabs(pinOffset1) > eps)
2385 {
2386 // 2(x1c-x0c)x1
2387 objectiveVector[puId1] += w * (pinOffset1 - pinOffset0);
2388 }
2389 }
2390 }

2996 inline std::vector<DesignInfo::DesignCell *> *
2997 findNeiborLUTFFsFromBinGrid(DesignInfo::DesignCell *curCell, float displacementUpperbound, int minNumNeighbor = 10)
2998 {
2999 // please note that the input DesignCell is only used to find the corresponding binGrid for site search.
3000 bool findLUT = curCell->isLUT();
3001 float targetX = cellId2location[curCell->getCellId()].X;
3002 float targetY = cellId2location[curCell->getCellId()].Y;
3003 std::vector<DesignInfo::DesignCell *> *res = new std::vector<DesignInfo::DesignCell *>();
3004 res->clear();
3005
3006 int binIdX, binIdY;
3007 getGridXY(targetX, targetY, binIdX, binIdY);
3008
3009 assert(binIdY >= 0);
3010 assert((unsigned int)binIdY < LUTFFBinGrid.size());
3011 assert(binIdX >= 0);
3012 assert((unsigned int)binIdX < LUTFFBinGrid[binIdY].size());
3013 assert(LUTFFBinGrid[binIdY][binIdX]->inRange(targetX, targetY));
3014
3015 std::queue<std::pair<int, int>> binXYqueue;
3016 std::set<std::pair<int, int>> reachedBinXYs;
3017 binXYqueue.emplace(binIdX, binIdY);
3018 reachedBinXYs.emplace(binIdX, binIdY);
3019
3020 bool findItself = false;
3021
3022 while (binXYqueue.size() > 0)
3023 {
3024 std::pair<int, int> curXY = binXYqueue.front();
3025 binXYqueue.pop();
3026 int curbinIdX = curXY.first, curbinIdY = curXY.second;
3027
3028 PlacementInfo::PlacementBinInfo *curBin = LUTFFBinGrid[curbinIdY][curbinIdX];
3029 float bin2TargetXYDistance = curBin->getManhattanDistanceTo(targetX, targetY);
3030 if (bin2TargetXYDistance > displacementUpperbound)
3031 continue;
3032 for (auto tmpCell : curBin->getCells())
3033 {
3034 if ((tmpCell->isLUT() && findLUT) || (tmpCell->isFF() && !findLUT))
3035 {
3036 float tmpX = cellId2location[tmpCell->getCellId()].X;
3037 float tmpY = cellId2location[tmpCell->getCellId()].Y;
3038 float tmpPUDis = fabs(targetX - tmpX) + y2xRatio * fabs(targetY - tmpY);
3039 if (tmpPUDis <= displacementUpperbound)
3040 {
3041 if (tmpCell == curCell)
3042 {
3043 findItself = true;
3044 }
3045 res->push_back(tmpCell);
3046 }
3047 }
3048 }
3049 assert(findItself);
3050 for (int nextY = curbinIdY - 1; nextY <= curbinIdY + 1; nextY++)
3051 {
3052 for (int nextX = curbinIdX - 1; nextX <= curbinIdX + 1; nextX++)
3053 {
3054 if (!(nextY >= 0))
3055 continue;
3056 if (!((unsigned int)nextY < LUTFFBinGrid.size()))
3057 continue;
3058 if (!(nextX >= 0))
3059 continue;
3060 if (!((unsigned int)nextX < LUTFFBinGrid[binIdY].size()))
3061 continue;
3062 PlacementInfo::PlacementBinInfo *nextBin = LUTFFBinGrid[nextY][nextX];
3063 float nextBin2TargetXYDistance = nextBin->getManhattanDistanceTo(targetX, targetY);
3064 if (nextBin2TargetXYDistance > displacementUpperbound)
3065 continue;
3066 std::pair<int, int> nextXY(nextX, nextY);
3067 if (reachedBinXYs.find(nextXY) == reachedBinXYs.end())
3068 {
3069 reachedBinXYs.insert(nextXY);
3070 binXYqueue.push(nextXY);
3071 }
3072 }
3073 }
3074 }
3075
3076 assert(findItself);
3077 return res;
3078 }

3108 inline PlacementUnit *getPlacementUnitByCell(DesignInfo::DesignCell *curCell)

3147 inline void addB2BNetInPlacementInfo(std::vector<Eigen::Triplet<float>> &objectiveMatrixTripletList,
3148 std::vector<float> &objectiveMatrixDiag, Eigen::VectorXd &objectiveVector,
3149 int puId0, int puId1, float pos0, float pos1, float pinOffset0,
3150 float pinOffset1, bool movable0, bool movable1, float w)
3151 {
3152 // min_x 0.5 * x'Px + q'x
3153 // s.t. l <= Ax <= u
3154 if (puId0 == puId1)
3155 return;
3156 if (movable0 && movable1)
3157 {
3158 // x0^2 + x1^2 - 2x0x1 + 2(x0c-x1c)x0 + 2(x1c-x0c)x1
3159 // objectiveMatrixTripletList.push_back(Eigen::Triplet<float>(puId0, puId0, w));
3160 // objectiveMatrixTripletList.push_back(Eigen::Triplet<float>(puId1, puId1, w));
3161 objectiveMatrixDiag[puId0] += w;
3162 objectiveMatrixDiag[puId1] += w;
3163 objectiveMatrixTripletList.push_back(Eigen::Triplet<float>(puId0, puId1, -w));
3164 objectiveMatrixTripletList.push_back(Eigen::Triplet<float>(puId1, puId0, -w));
3165 if (fabs(pinOffset0) > eps || fabs(pinOffset1) > eps)
3166 {
3167 // 2(x0c-x1c)x0 + 2(x1c-x0c)x1
3168 objectiveVector[puId0] += w * (pinOffset0 - pinOffset1);
3169 objectiveVector[puId1] += w * (pinOffset1 - pinOffset0);
3170 }
3171 }
3172 else if (movable0)
3173 {
3174 // x0^2 - 2x0x1 + 2(x0c-x1c)x0
3175 // objectiveMatrixTripletList.push_back(Eigen::Triplet<float>(puId0, puId0, w));
3176 objectiveMatrixDiag[puId0] += w;
3177 objectiveVector[puId0] += -w * pos1;
3178 if (fabs(pinOffset0) > eps || fabs(pinOffset1) > eps)
3179 {
3180 // 2(x0c-x1c)x0
3181 objectiveVector[puId0] += w * (pinOffset0 - pinOffset1);
3182 }
3183 }
3184 else if (movable1)
3185 {
3186 // x1^2 - 2x0x1 + 2(x1c-x0c)x1
3187 // objectiveMatrixTripletList.push_back(Eigen::Triplet<float>(puId1, puId1, w));
3188 objectiveMatrixDiag[puId1] += w;
3189 objectiveVector[puId1] += -w * pos0;
3190 if (fabs(pinOffset0) > eps || fabs(pinOffset1) > eps)
3191 {
3192 // 2(x1c-x0c)x1
3193 objectiveVector[puId1] += w * (pinOffset1 - pinOffset0);
3194 }
3195 }
3196 }
3197
3216 inline void addPseudoNetsInPlacementInfo(std::vector<Eigen::Triplet<float>> &objectiveMatrixTripletList,
3217 std::vector<float> &objectiveMatrixDiag, Eigen::VectorXd &objectiveVector,
3218 PlacementUnit *tmpPU, float targetLoc, float pseudoWeight, float y2xRatio,
3219 bool updateX, bool updateY)
3220 {
3221 assert(updateX ^ updateY);
3222 if (updateY)
3223 {
3224 pseudoWeight *= y2xRatio;
3225 }
3226 bool movable = !tmpPU->isFixed();
3227 if (movable)
3228 {
3229 addB2BNetInPlacementInfo(objectiveMatrixTripletList, objectiveMatrixDiag, objectiveVector, tmpPU->getId(),
3230 -1, targetLoc, targetLoc, 0, 0, true, false, pseudoWeight);
3231 }
3232 }

3440 inline bool isLegalLocation(DesignInfo::DesignCell *curCell, float targetX, float targetY)
3441 {
3442 auto curPU = cellId2PlacementUnit[curCell->getCellId()];
3443
3444 if (curPU->getType() == PlacementUnitType_UnpackedCell)
3445 {
3446 float fX = targetX;
3447 float fY = targetY;
3448 fX = std::max(globalMinX + eps, (std::min(fX, globalMaxX - eps)));
3449 fY = std::max(globalMinY + eps, (std::min(fY, globalMaxY - eps)));
3450 return (std::fabs(fX - targetX) + std::fabs(fY - targetY)) < eps;
3451 }
3452 else if (auto curMacro = dynamic_cast<PlacementMacro *>(curPU))
3453 {
3454 float offsetX = curMacro->getCellOffsetXInMacro(curCell);
3455 float offsetY = curMacro->getCellOffsetYInMacro(curCell);
3456 float fX = targetX - offsetX;
3457 float fY = targetY - offsetY;
3458 if (fY + curMacro->getTopOffset() > globalMaxY - eps)
3459 {
3460 fY = (globalMaxY - 2 * eps) - curMacro->getTopOffset();
3461 }
3462 else if (fY + curMacro->getBottomOffset() < globalMinY + eps)
3463 {
3464 fY = (globalMinY + 2 * eps) - curMacro->getBottomOffset();
3465 }
3466
3467 if (fX + curMacro->getRightOffset() > globalMaxX - eps)
3468 {
3469 fX = (globalMaxX - 2 * eps) - curMacro->getRightOffset();
3470 }
3471 else if (fX + curMacro->getLeftOffset() < globalMinX + eps)
3472 {
3473 fX = (globalMinX + 2 * eps) - curMacro->getLeftOffset();
3474 }
3475 return (std::fabs(fX + offsetX - targetX) + std::fabs(fY + offsetY - targetY)) < eps;
3476 }
3477 else
3478 {
3479 assert(false && "should not reach here");
3480 return false;
3481 }

3786 inline std::vector<DeviceInfo::DeviceSite *> *
3787 findNeiborSiteFromBinGrid(DesignInfo::DesignCell *curCell, float targetX, float targetY,
3788 float displacementThreshold, int siteNumThreshold, bool checkClockRegion = false)
3789 {
3790 // please note that the input DesignCell is only used to find the corresponding binGrid for site search.
3791 std::vector<DeviceInfo::DeviceSite *> *res = new std::vector<DeviceInfo::DeviceSite *>(0);
3792
3793 int binIdX, binIdY;
3794 getGridXY(targetX, targetY, binIdX, binIdY);
3795 auto curPU = getPlacementUnitByCellId(curCell->getCellId());
3796 int targetClockRegionX = -1;
3797 if (PU2ClockRegionColumn.find(curPU) != PU2ClockRegionColumn.end() && checkClockRegion)
3798 {
3799 targetClockRegionX = PU2ClockRegionColumn[curPU];
3800 }
3801
3802 while (res->size() == 0)
3803 {
3804 auto sharedTypeIds = getPotentialBELTypeIDs(curCell->getCellType());
3805
3806 for (auto sharedTypeId : sharedTypeIds)
3807 {
3808 assert((unsigned int)curCell->getCellId() < cellId2CellBinInfo.size());
3809 assert(binIdY >= 0);
3810 assert((unsigned int)binIdY < SharedBELTypeBinGrid[sharedTypeId].size());
3811 assert(binIdX >= 0);
3812 assert((unsigned int)binIdX < SharedBELTypeBinGrid[sharedTypeId][binIdY].size());
3813
3814 std::vector<std::vector<PlacementBinInfo *>> &curBinGrid = SharedBELTypeBinGrid[sharedTypeId];
3815
3816 std::queue<std::pair<int, int>> binXYqueue;
3817 std::set<std::pair<int, int>> reachedBinXYs;
3818 binXYqueue.emplace(binIdX, binIdY);
3819 reachedBinXYs.emplace(binIdX, binIdY);
3820
3821 while (binXYqueue.size() > 0)
3822 {
3823 std::pair<int, int> curXY = binXYqueue.front();
3824 binXYqueue.pop();
3825 int curbinIdX = curXY.first, curbinIdY = curXY.second;
3826
3827 PlacementBinInfo *curBin = curBinGrid[curbinIdY][curbinIdX];
3828 float bin2TargetXYDistance = curBin->getManhattanDistanceTo(targetX, targetY);
3829 if (bin2TargetXYDistance > displacementThreshold)
3830 continue;
3831 int findSiteCnt = 0;
3832 for (auto curSite : curBin->getCorrespondingSites())
3833 {
3834 if (!curSite->isOccupied() && !curSite->isMapped())
3835 {
3836 if (getDisplacement(targetX, targetY, curSite) < displacementThreshold)
3837 {
3838 findSiteCnt++;
3839 if (targetClockRegionX >= 0 && targetClockRegionX != curSite->getClockRegionX())
3840 continue;
3841 res->push_back(curSite);
3842 }
3843 }
3844 }
3845
3846 if (res->size() < (unsigned int)siteNumThreshold)
3847 {
3848 for (int nextY = curbinIdY - 1; nextY <= curbinIdY + 1; nextY++)
3849 {
3850 for (int nextX = curbinIdX - 1; nextX <= curbinIdX + 1; nextX++)
3851 {
3852 if (!(nextY >= 0))
3853 continue;
3854 if (!((unsigned int)nextY < SharedBELTypeBinGrid[sharedTypeId].size()))
3855 continue;
3856 if (!(nextX >= 0))
3857 continue;
3858 if (!((unsigned int)nextX < SharedBELTypeBinGrid[sharedTypeId][binIdY].size()))
3859 continue;
3860 PlacementBinInfo *nextBin = curBinGrid[nextY][nextX];
3861 float nextBin2TargetXYDistance = nextBin->getManhattanDistanceTo(targetX, targetY);
3862 if (nextBin2TargetXYDistance > displacementThreshold)
3863 continue;
3864 std::pair<int, int> nextXY(nextX, nextY);
3865 if (reachedBinXYs.find(nextXY) == reachedBinXYs.end())
3866 {
3867 reachedBinXYs.insert(nextXY);
3868 binXYqueue.push(nextXY);
3869 }
3870 }
3871 }
3872 }
3873 }
3874 }
3875 displacementThreshold *= 1.5;
3876 }
3877
3878 return res;
3879 }

3927 double getTotalHPWL()
3928 {

3931 //#pragma omp parallel for reduction(+ : totalHPWL)
3932 for (int netId = 0; netId < numNet; netId++)

4115 inline unsigned int getPairPinNum(DesignInfo::DesignCell *LUTA, DesignInfo::DesignCell *LUTB)
4116 {
4117 if (LUTA->getInputPins().size() == 6 || LUTB->getInputPins().size() == 6 || LUTA->isLUT6() || LUTB->isLUT6())
4118 return 12;
4119
4120 int pinNumA = 0;
4121 int totalPin = 0;
4122 int netIds[5]; // be aware that a LUT might have pins connected to the same net and they should be treated as
4123 // different inputs.
4124
4125 for (auto tmpPin : LUTA->getInputPins())
4126 {
4127 if (!tmpPin->isUnconnected())
4128 {
4129 netIds[pinNumA] = tmpPin->getNet()->getElementIdInType();
4130 pinNumA++;
4131 }
4132 }
4133 totalPin = pinNumA;
4134 for (auto tmpPin : LUTB->getInputPins())
4135 {
4136 if (!tmpPin->isUnconnected())
4137 {
4138 bool matched = false;
4139 for (int i = 0; i < pinNumA; i++)
4140 {
4141 if (netIds[i] >= 0 && netIds[i] == tmpPin->getNet()->getElementIdInType())
4142 {
4143 netIds[i] = -1;
4144 matched = true;
4145 break;
4146 }
4147 }
4148 if (!matched)
4149 {
4150 totalPin++;
4151 }
4152 }
4153 }
4154 return totalPin;
4155 }
